<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_df8915be-e1e4-4714-bb04-cf32c82b27d1" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S32C2</sptc><title id="_b966c200-2416-4211-8e11-41c01764135b">Separation of stage areas, etc</title><archive-num>2019: Spec H1.3: 2</archive-num><subclause id="_253ca4a2-e6b1-48eb-8cab-3ae5ee98bf18" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e2e172cf-ac14-4a8a-8760-054b289824b3">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Dressing rooms, scene docks, property rooms, workshops, associated store rooms and other ancillary areas must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_dcc30c27-5fd1-4059-b8f4-b2e9cf12e24a">located on the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1478_0.4.0.xml#_02701ef9-5783-4b2b-af0e-4a764b0375ed" id="_163874b1-eaa1-4837-ba8c-9181af6bcac1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">stage</xref> side of the proscenium wall; and</li><li id="_801c15c1-0d6d-4ed6-b5a2-a2bed114c01d">separated from corridors and the like by construction having an FRL of not less than 60/60/60, and if of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1359_0.4.0.xml#_2cf43983-ddc7-4b7f-b16e-2d3ed619886e" id="_7869690e-637f-4380-a3b4-9d1eadc43754" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">lightweight construction</xref>, complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/141_0.8.0.xml#_e5ff9fe3-2084-4425-9e49-c8d7f5717cda" id="_f00f7746-b30c-43e1-9863-fd6704bbf39a" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 6</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_b77cd6a1-185d-4a91-8a75-1534046e0c6d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2689db68-d35b-4354-8666-c17a7e135f2d">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1478_0.4.0.xml#_02701ef9-5783-4b2b-af0e-4a764b0375ed" id="_140eff0b-1807-44bd-a86a-70dd8cfcb8fd" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">stage</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1207_1.0.0.xml#_a664353a-ef5b-4cd2-b68b-f2db1db81dce" id="_2ffe9f0e-51fb-4c38-abdf-0d8c31696224" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">backstage</xref> must be separated from other parts of the building other than the audience seating area by construction having an FRL of not less than 60/60/60, and if of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1359_0.4.0.xml#_2cf43983-ddc7-4b7f-b16e-2d3ed619886e" id="_55002ff7-741c-4342-9b62-cfdaa34fc8d0" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">lightweight construction</xref>, complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/141_0.8.0.xml#_e5ff9fe3-2084-4425-9e49-c8d7f5717cda" id="_aa3dac81-ade4-4b75-a13b-5ccbbef89a6c" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 6</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f829c537-cb24-4da2-9495-71c8637e7f9a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c29ced84-4e6c-4a5a-a56b-f3fa489eff39">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Any doorway in the construction referred to in (1) and (2) must be protected by a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1449_26.3.0.xml#_7f0d37c8-f244-4a83-9a76-6ece85e1e430" id="_e249985e-24e5-46fd-85d2-b97b4f082cfe" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">self-closing</xref> –/60/30 fire door.</p></subclause></clause>